OL,7,FAs he disqualified the Tory
OL,8,Fenvironmentalist from driving,
OL,9,FDistrict Judge Daniel Sternberg warned
OL,10,Fthat drivers who speed "emit more
OL,11,Fharmful emissions" even in hybrid and
OL,12,Felectric cars.
OL,14,FThe court heard that in April last
OL,15,Fyear, Lord Goldsmith was caught
OL,16,Fdriving at 29mph in a 20 zone on
OL,17,FChelsea Embankment, and in July he
OL,18,Fdrove at 28mph in a 20 zone near
OL,19,FKensington Gardens.
