OL,7,FThe former MP for Richmond Park, who
OL,8,Funsuccessfully ran to be London mayor
OL,9,Fin 2016 before serving as a minister
OL,10,Fin Boris Johnson's cabinet, did not
OL,11,Fattend the hearing.
OL,13,FBenjamin Waidhofer, defending, said
OL,14,FLord Goldsmith had shown "remorse" for
OL,15,Fhis offending and is "not someone who
OL,16,Fis manifestly defying the usual speed
OL,17,Flimits".
